data.description: Back on the Market at NO FAULT to Seller. Enjoy privacy as you enter this Gated Community with Pool, Dog Park , Club House, Fishing in the Lake and Walking Paths. This home is a open concept contemporary style with lots of privacy. Master is on the 2nd Level and two additional bedrooms on the bottom level with a shared bath and its own private patio. On the main level you find a huge family room with a fireplace eat in kitcehn and laundry. All new appliances that stay with the home and updated cabinets and counter tops in the Kitchen. Both full baths have recently been updated. Schedule your personal tour today!! Hoa includes  Yard Maintenance, Cable/Internet , Clubhouse, Common Area Maintenance, , Pool, Pest Control for Termites and Exterior Maintenance.
